oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Rear of 316 Wilburn Street, c.1950s
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Photograph of the rear of 316 Wilburn Street in East Nashville after rehabilitation, circa 1950s. The house was rehabilitated as part of the East Nashville Urban Renewal Project (Project Tenn. R-13). Photographed by the Nashville Housing Authority. Forms part of the MDHA Photograph Collection. 1 photograph : b & w.
